  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_nhs_standard_contract">NHS Standard Contract</xref>
 is for use when commissioning healthcare services (other than those commissioned under primary care contracts) and is adaptable for use for a broad range of 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_service">SERVICES</xref>
 and delivery models.        </p>
      <p>
         <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_nhs_england">NHS England</xref>
 is responsible for the preparation and publication of the 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_nhs_standard_contract">NHS Standard Contract</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
For further information on the 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_nhs_standard_contract">NHS Standard Contract</xref>, see the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_nhs_england">NHS England</xref>
 website at: 
              <xref href="https://www.england.nhs.uk/nhs-standard-contract/"
               scope="external"
               format="html">NHS standard contract</xref>.        </p>
  </div>
